{"tid":707753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[土地] 九龍塘做低密度豪宅區根本係錯誤","createTime":"2018-06-19T00:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T07:53:57.000Z","uid":147226,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"19bedfa1bb8494b6c9fdcb6ecec5ab74a11fc9aa","tid":707753,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:22:36.000Z","msg":"尋日睇咗個樓盤節目，介紹九龍塘啲獨立屋，叫價億幾兩億咁，諗住一世都無機會住成億嘅樓就睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個節目一影埋個窗，哇頂，唔係望隔離學校、隔離屋就係馬路，啲景仲差過公屋<br />\n<br />\n以前睇過啲幾千萬豪宅，半山又好、淺水灣又好，唔係高高在上，就係陽光與海灘<br />\n<br />\n諗落九龍塘兩樣都無，唯一九龍塘最好果樣叫交通方便，但同啲有錢佬有咩關係<br />\n<br />\n唔係話仇富，但剷晒九龍塘啲低密度高宅，做高密度私樓，再降低半山啲密度俾呢班有錢佬唔係仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根本就 win-win"},{"pid":"1881a3308c84496c1504b3f09ee9f0ca8d49c585","tid":707753,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:33:01.000Z","msg":"最美的風景是冇人"},{"pid":"dc8bd4c88a831970eaa6010c1c038b7b12620089","tid":707753,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:46:45.000Z","msg":"傻仔，住過你就明架喇"},{"pid":"9e02e7660107768218030d9d88a1fb796459a3b0","tid":707753,"uid":54929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc8bd4c88a831970eaa6010c1c038b7b12620089","tid":707753,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:46:45.000Z","msg":"傻仔，住過你就明架喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:48:40.000Z","msg":"係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cede5c5c450fa05976cd90037c0d9bfabf9ff6","tid":707753,"uid":25952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:54:10.000Z","msg":"唔係有個好校網既話 應該無人想住個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73657050ed7de7a1448091430e8e0f8cd1fb4c7b","tid":707753,"uid":31796,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dc8bd4c88a831970eaa6010c1c038b7b12620089","tid":707753,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:46:45.000Z","msg":"傻仔，住過你就明架喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:55:24.000Z","msg":"你係咪訓過幾個鐘當住過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a988e111cd09a22662f84f72b4b26bdd7dda98f1","tid":707753,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:10:36.000Z","msg":"有錢就會要私隱度"},{"pid":"4170ab8407313c5b1aa33ff0cfba04766d893cd1","tid":707753,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc8bd4c88a831970eaa6010c1c038b7b12620089","tid":707753,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:46:45.000Z","msg":"傻仔，住過你就明架喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:33:12.000Z","msg":"咁我認住唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我有兩億真係寧願住半山/淺水灣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋全香港其中一個交通最方便嘅位，起低密度真係好浪費"},{"pid":"a2c0dd1a7a9be3c528945fb87ff5254c8a65d13e","tid":707753,"uid":15644,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"真係有錢根本唔會住九龍塘<br />\n<br />\n九龍塘係比班唔夠有錢既有錢人住"},{"pid":"9cc972b0dfb97ca7e4e0e157c8bfeaf8453a78b2","tid":707753,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"畢架山一號好好景喎 仲望到銅鑼灣 <br />\n利申住畢架山隔離嘅城大宿舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時睇到幻彩詠香江"},{"pid":"59576af061d78f974d8fe8328b47e012f3157400","tid":707753,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2c0dd1a7a9be3c528945fb87ff5254c8a65d13e","tid":707753,"uid":15644,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"真係有錢根本唔會住九龍塘<br />\n<br />\n九龍塘係比班唔夠有錢既有錢人住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"真係有錢既住晒公屋啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124cf4101f01beaa9a5b5dd59d06d2d5ada63e59","tid":707753,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"五六十年前規劃落 果時仲係香港後花園 又大直路落尖沙咀 而家間間屋都幾億 收地成本幾貴先得架 同埋其實內街同又一村果啲環境幾好 直頭都唔覺係九龍"}]}